title: North Harbor Tower Featuring  large Studio up for 7 month sublease
posting_body: ["Located in Lakeshore East, North Harbor Tower's desirable location places the city at your doorstep.", 'Our 360 degree views of Chicago, Lake Michigan and access to all the Near East Side action will provide you with the ultimate Chicago experience.', 'Come home every day to a studio, floor plan with modern custom design, stunning airy bay windows and beautifully appointed amenities including an indoor heated pool, professional fitness center and expansive outdoor courtyard.', 'Your home was inspired by you, for you.', 'Delivering a balanced, fulfilling lifestyle at our residence is one of our top priorities.', 'Our community features a 24 hour door attendant, 24 hour maintenance, on-site management and friendly, attentive staff that is always ready and willing to help.', 'We invite you to schedule a visit to learn more about our distinct version of Chicago luxury apartment living.', 'Rent vary depending on lessening office ******']
